        "text": "主說：“先前的事，我從古時就預言過了， 已經從我的口裡說出來了，又說給人聽了； 我忽然行事，事情就都成就了。"
      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "主說：早先的事，我從古時說明， 已經出了我的口， 也是我所指示的； 我忽然行做，事便成就。"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "I declared the former things long ago And they went forth from My mouth, and I proclaimed them. Suddenly I acted, and they came to pass."
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "I foretold the former things long ago, my mouth announced them and I made them known; then suddenly I acted, and they came to pass."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Long ago I told you what was going to happen. Then suddenly I took action, and all my predictions came true."
      }
